        <div class="executive-summary">
            <h3>üéØ Assessment Overview</h3>
            <p>This report documents intentional security misconfigurations across AWS, Azure, and Google Cloud Platform environments. The lab demonstrates common cloud security vulnerabilities found in real-world deployments, serving as a comprehensive training resource for security professionals.</p>
            
            <h4>Key Findings:</h4>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Critical Risk Issues:</strong> 45+ findings across all platforms</li>
                <li><strong>Network Security:</strong> Overpermissive firewall rules exposing services globally</li>
                <li><strong>Identity & Access:</strong> Wildcard permissions and excessive privileges</li>
                <li><strong>Data Protection:</strong> Unencrypted storage and public access configurations</li>
                <li><strong>Monitoring Gaps:</strong> Disabled logging and audit trails</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
