        <div class="executive-summary">
            <h3>üîç Key Patterns Across Platforms</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Network Exposure:</strong> All platforms show overpermissive firewall/security group rules</li>
                <li><strong>IAM Overpermissioning:</strong> Wildcard permissions and excessive privileges common</li>
                <li><strong>Public Resources:</strong> Storage, databases, and compute instances exposed to internet</li>
                <li><strong>Encryption Gaps:</strong> Data at rest and in transit encryption disabled</li>
                <li><strong>Monitoring Blindness:</strong> Audit logging and security monitoring disabled</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h4>üéØ Training Value</h4>
            <p>This lab environment demonstrates over 90 distinct security misconfigurations across 35 cloud services, providing comprehensive hands-on experience with:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Cloud Security Posture Management (CSPM) tool validation</li>
                <li>Security assessment methodology development</li>
                <li>Cloud security best practices training</li>
                <li>Incident response and remediation exercises</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
